	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2016-07-05T00:11:03">Acxiom Corporation (Acxiom) is a technology and enablement services company. The Company operates through three business segments: Marketing Services, Audience Solutions, and Connectivity. The Company's Marketing Services segment helps clients to unify data at individual level. The Audience Solutions segment helps clients to validate the accuracy of their people-based data, enhance it with additional insight and keep it up to date, enabling clients to reach desired audiences with relevant messages. The Connectivity segment activates data and makes it portable across the open marketing ecosystem. The Company serves a global client base from locations in the United States, Europe and the Asia-Pacific region. The Company's client base includes organizations in these regions across industry verticals, including financial, insurance and investment services, automotive, retail, telecommunications, healthcare, travel, entertainment, non-profit and government.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2017-08-16T14:35:19">BRIEF: For the three months ended 30 June 2017, Acxiom Corporation revenues decreased 1% to $212.5M. Net loss totaled $1.3M vs. income of $4M. Revenues reflect Marketing and Data Services segment decrease of 17% to $91.6M. Net loss reflects Marketing and Data Services segment income decrease of 2% to $19.8M, connectivity segment loss totaling $48K vs. income of $291K.</Text>
	</TextInfo>
